Chemistry Lab Bench
===================

The reaction-engine pattern and declarative reaction-rule schema in this game
(src/domain/reaction.ts, src/contracts/experiment.ts) are adapted to TypeScript
from the MIT-licensed project:

    chem_lab — https://github.com/nsriram/chem_lab
    Copyright (c) nsriram, MIT License

Only the engine pattern (first-match-wins rule registry resolving a vessel +
action to a reaction result) and the rule-schema shape were ported. The original
project's AS-level chemistry content, exam-marking engine, i18n, PDF export, and
DOM/emoji UI are not used here. The NCERT Class 9 curriculum content, the
mobile-first Canvas presentation, and the experiment data are original to this
project.
